    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_how_title">How it works</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_how_summary">"Crossfade overlaps the end of one song with the start of the next, fading one down as the other comes up over your chosen duration and curve.

It runs on auto-advance (when a song ends on its own) and on manual skips — each has its own toggle above. On auto-advance the blend starts a few seconds before the song ends.

Requires YouTube Music 9.x or newer."</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_best_title">Works best with</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_best_summary">Normal song-to-song playback and auto-advance, repeat-one (the song crossfades into itself), and local audio — phone speaker, wired headphones, Bluetooth, or USB.</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_quirks_title">Doesn\'t work quite right</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_quirks_summary">"Music videos play as audio-only while crossfade is on (long-press shuffle to pause if you want the video)

Songs shorter than your fade duration may skip the fade

The lock screen or notification can briefly show a stale state mid-transition"</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_known_title">Known issues</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_known_summary">"A music video set as the first song — or one started from outside the current queue — may briefly show as video before audio-only mode kicks in

Pausing crossfade to watch a music video can leave some videos black (the ones whose audio comes from the video itself). Pausing crossfade before you pick the song avoids it"</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_unsupported_title">Doesn\'t work at all</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_unsupported_summary">"Casting or mirroring audio (Chromecast, screen or audio mirroring) — crossfade pauses because it's unstable there and may never be fixable.

YouTube Music 8.x — crossfade only runs on 9.x and newer"</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_credit_title">Credit</string>
    <string name="morphe_music_crossfade_about_credit_summary">Crossfade feature by VazerOG</string>

